- Vercel DNS `brain.joelclaw.com` A → 100.113.161.65 created ~17:55Z — **by a concurrent flagg-side session, not this one** (this session's ssh to flagg is publickey-denied from blaine; the DNS record and Caddy edits require flagg-local or Vercel-authed hands, and Vercel CLI here confirmed the record exists).
